      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CRITICALLY (1) is still a maiden after nine runs but rarely far away, the latest filling a minor placing when second at Shepparton. In the money at the last three runs. Good form should continue. JASPER ONE (5) is long overdue and boasts a solid record despite not having won his maiden yet, the latest finishing fourth at this track. Has ability and can measure up. GREYSCALE (2) shows ability but remains a maiden after seven starts. Is better than last start when out of the placings, finishing sixth (25.01) at Sale. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Great chance to atone. SOUL SECRET (7) is by Aussie Secret out of Dyna Sarah making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can feature with the right run.",
